<head>EUNUCH</head>
    <list type="translations">
        <item xml:lang="zh">太監</item>
        <item xml:lang="och">寺人</item>
    </list>
<div type="definition">
<p>CASTRATED MALE OFFICIAL GOVERNING A HAREM.</p>
    </div>
<div type="notes">
<div type="old-chinese-criteria">
<p>1. The standard term for a eunuch is sì rén 寺人.</p>
        </div>
<div type="modern-chinese-criteria">
<p>閹寺 is the most explicit current word for a eunuch.</p>
<p>閹宦</p>
<p>太監 refers specifically to the palace eunuch.</p>
<p>黃門</p>
<p>宦官</p>
<p>監</p>
<p>內臣</p>
<p>rough draft to BEGIN TO identify synonym group members for analysis, based on CL etc. 18.11.2003. CH ／</p>
        </div>
